modName: Colorful Forsworn Female Head Dress Retexture
summary: Makes the female headdress more colorful and interesting. Simple retexture, 2x original resolution.
descriptionHtml:
I love the original headress, but I prefer a more colorful look to head dresses, so I made the feathers colorful and added golden beads in the dreads. I also made the horns less yellow and more bone color so the dress looks more dynamic.

2x original resolution. 

female forsworn headress has been modified to be more colorful. Simple retexture. 

Simply download with manager and enjoy :D
author: chocolambot
